{"id":596066,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【立此存照】严夫人后继：陈婧妍妈妈/","date":"2018-09-21T10:08:49Z","modified":"2018-09-21T15:34:28Z","title":"【立此存照】严夫人后继：陈婧妍妈妈","content":"<p>9月21日，网传一则“陈婧妍妈妈”与“廖老师”微信聊天对话，在图中自称为“陈婧妍妈妈”的家长为向老师展示自己家庭的“人脉关系”，将自己丈夫、表姐夫、父亲的高中学生等一众任职官员的详细信息告知老师，最终不知何原因流传网络。该事件与此前的“严夫人事件”相似，均为官员亲属“显摆式”展示“关系能量”引起关注。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq49gspj20a90m8gmz.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-596072\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq49gspj20a90m8gmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"369\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq49gspj20a90m8gmz.jpg 369w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq49gspj20a90m8gmz-138x300.jpg 138w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" /></a></p>\n<p>目前，几位“亲属”的职位信息已得到网友查证。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-596066 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%b8%a5%e5%a4%ab%e4%ba%ba%e5%90%8e%e7%bb%a7%ef%bc%9a%e9%99%88%e5%a9%a7%e5%a6%8d%e5%a6%88%e5%a6%88/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq4q1z7j20qo1bgtbk/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/bcb42b7cly1fvgaq4q1z7j20qo1bgtbk-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"ht